WEBVTT

01:40.740 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.190 --> 01:48.810
[Episode 19]

01:53.130 --> 01:55.789
Help me take a look—
which one do I look better in?

02:00.970 --> 02:02.970
Or do you think my figure

02:03.000 --> 02:04.330
looks good in anything?

02:09.490 --> 02:10.210
Mu.

02:11.330 --> 02:12.130
What's wrong?

03:00.330 --> 03:01.860
It's not the right time yet.

03:54.280 --> 03:55.000
Come here.

04:10.890 --> 04:11.950
Don't you feel hot?

04:12.080 --> 04:12.960
A little.

04:13.560 --> 04:15.890
You're already hot and still this clingy?

04:16.899 --> 04:19.230
You're the one who's clingy, not me, okay?

04:30.440 --> 04:32.080
Has the race time been set?

04:34.340 --> 04:35.440
Yeah, it's coming up soon.

04:35.440 --> 04:38.170
Are you still racing against
Mr. Wan and his team?

04:40.290 --> 04:42.020
This race is also a chance for me

04:42.930 --> 04:45.130
to settle my issues with Wan Shengbang.

04:47.030 --> 04:48.550
What kind of race is it?

04:51.050 --> 04:52.510
A mountain obstacle race.

04:52.730 --> 04:53.800
An obstacle race?

04:54.560 --> 04:56.000
Isn't that dangerous?

04:59.780 --> 05:01.640
I can get the map and the locations

05:01.680 --> 05:03.260
of the obstacles in advance.

05:03.260 --> 05:04.460
I'll just avoid them.

05:05.730 --> 05:06.730
How did you get it?

05:07.370 --> 05:08.500
Through Officer Lu.

05:09.200 --> 05:10.760
Officer Lu?

05:13.690 --> 05:15.250
So you mean

05:16.000 --> 05:18.000
besides you, there are other people

05:18.410 --> 05:21.470
in the organization
who're also assisting Officer Lu?

05:23.090 --> 05:25.450
Who are they? Do you know them?

05:26.770 --> 05:29.100
Those accomplices hiding in the shadows.

05:29.450 --> 05:30.370
"Those

05:30.780 --> 05:32.840
accomplices hiding in the shadows?"

05:36.159 --> 05:37.560
What kind of talk is that?

05:38.380 --> 05:39.840
It's not that mysterious.

05:43.330 --> 05:45.590
We just each get what we need, that's all.

05:46.120 --> 05:48.610
To get to the bottom of
the smuggling gang,

05:49.170 --> 05:50.820
since I'm leading the charge,

05:50.820 --> 05:53.360
surely I need people
to cooperate from behind.

05:53.360 --> 05:55.620
Each person serves a different purpose.

05:56.560 --> 05:58.560
These matters are quite sensitive,

05:58.800 --> 06:00.800
and if we're going to
keep working in this line,

06:00.800 --> 06:02.730
no one wants to expose themselves.

06:04.560 --> 06:05.000
So...

06:05.030 --> 06:07.490
Has your detective spirit
taken over again?

06:07.680 --> 06:09.140
Aren't you going to sleep?

06:49.990 --> 06:51.700
I can't let Mu join me

06:52.680 --> 06:55.140
in living that precarious life
I had before.

06:56.230 --> 06:57.890
I have to win tomorrow's race,

06:58.170 --> 06:59.440
no matter what.

07:00.970 --> 07:02.000
Only by winning

07:02.440 --> 07:04.170
can I bring an end to all of this,

07:04.410 --> 07:05.440
and only then

07:05.730 --> 07:07.660
can I be with Mu openly and cleanly.

07:08.210 --> 07:09.360
I owe her this.

07:10.880 --> 07:11.650
Mu.

07:12.520 --> 07:13.760
Don't worry about me.

07:14.800 --> 07:15.680
For you,

07:16.880 --> 07:18.340
I will return victorious.

07:20.280 --> 07:20.970
Dad.

07:21.880 --> 07:22.560
Mom.

07:23.490 --> 07:25.620
If you can see me from wherever you are,

07:26.360 --> 07:28.020
please bless me with success,

07:28.940 --> 07:30.140
and bless me and Mu.

08:32.850 --> 08:36.280
[Speeding Auto House]

09:25.450 --> 09:26.980
Yang took the day off today.

09:28.360 --> 09:30.290
I need to go take care of something.

09:31.380 --> 09:32.780
I might be back a bit late.

09:36.680 --> 09:38.080
Don't worry. Sleep well.

09:40.190 --> 09:41.990
Remember to eat when you wake up.

09:54.440 --> 09:55.160
Be good.

10:03.620 --> 10:05.150
I'll take you out tomorrow,

10:05.300 --> 10:06.090
okay?

11:36.750 --> 11:38.160
I have something for you.

11:42.810 --> 11:44.450
This is a set of racing gear.

11:44.890 --> 11:46.530
It's fireproof and heat-resistant,

11:46.530 --> 11:48.770
kind of a safety measure.

11:51.720 --> 11:53.210
What, do you think

11:53.580 --> 11:54.580
I need this?

11:55.990 --> 11:57.610
No matter what kind of race it is,

11:57.610 --> 11:58.740
safety comes first.

11:58.790 --> 12:00.920
This underground race you're entering

12:00.920 --> 12:03.470
has high speeds and complex tracks,

12:03.880 --> 12:06.210
and there's no emergency technical team.

12:06.800 --> 12:07.770
But

12:10.370 --> 12:13.770
this can buy you 20 seconds.

12:25.670 --> 12:26.730
I'm not that fussy,

12:28.010 --> 12:30.010
but I appreciate your kind gesture.

12:30.390 --> 12:31.040
Thanks.

14:25.250 --> 14:27.910
Zhao said he needed to go
take care of something.

14:28.740 --> 14:29.540
It seems

14:30.080 --> 14:31.650
that decisive race

14:32.140 --> 14:33.670
is likely happening today.

14:46.050 --> 14:46.850
Where are you?

14:48.520 --> 14:49.360
You're up?

14:50.490 --> 14:51.400
You promised

14:51.910 --> 14:53.640
to take me out tomorrow, right?

14:57.920 --> 14:58.710
I'll try.

14:59.480 --> 15:00.770
You promised me.

15:01.480 --> 15:03.140
You can't go back on your word.

15:05.650 --> 15:07.110
If you break your promise,

15:07.680 --> 15:09.490
I'll never speak to you again.

15:09.880 --> 15:10.720
Got it.

16:27.770 --> 16:28.650
Jiang Mu?

16:30.760 --> 16:32.020
Why are you still here?

16:35.320 --> 16:36.520
Where else could I go?

17:50.240 --> 17:51.370
Can I talk to you?

17:51.770 --> 17:52.970
About Brandy's race,

17:53.010 --> 17:54.140
how much do you know?

17:54.810 --> 17:56.030
Could Liang Yanfeng also be

17:56.030 --> 17:57.420
part of the alliance?

17:59.290 --> 18:00.710
Why are you asking me this?

18:00.710 --> 18:02.110
I need you to come with me.

18:03.670 --> 18:04.810
Why should I trust you?

18:04.810 --> 18:06.340
I can't reach him right now.

18:06.670 --> 18:07.690
If you want to save Brandy's life,

18:07.690 --> 18:09.010
you must come with me.

18:12.320 --> 18:14.850
How do I know
you're not just trying to fool me?

18:19.050 --> 18:22.180
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

18:23.300 --> 18:25.940
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

18:25.940 --> 18:27.670
It was Lu who sent me to find you.

18:30.460 --> 18:31.460
Can we go now?

18:33.770 --> 18:35.170
Where are you taking her?

18:38.810 --> 18:39.730
Sanlai.

18:41.890 --> 18:43.620
Jin Zhao seems to be in trouble.

18:46.130 --> 18:46.950
I'll go with you.

18:46.950 --> 18:47.810
You can't come.

18:48.400 --> 18:50.200
You're not part of the alliance.

18:53.430 --> 18:55.050
Then turn on your phone's location.

18:55.050 --> 18:57.710
I'm worried you won't be able to
handle it alone.

19:01.340 --> 19:02.540
What happened to him?

19:03.650 --> 19:05.180
About what Brandy is doing,

19:05.240 --> 19:06.770
how much do you really know?

19:07.000 --> 19:08.090
Only the basics.

19:09.680 --> 19:11.680
He can't follow the original route.

19:11.770 --> 19:12.890
What do you mean?

19:16.630 --> 19:19.130
Someone suspects
there's an undercover cop in the alliance.

19:19.130 --> 19:20.830
They can't identify who it is yet.

19:20.830 --> 19:22.160
If he follows the original route,

19:22.160 --> 19:23.090
he's done for.

19:27.960 --> 19:30.280
The one who provided him
with the route map

19:30.280 --> 19:31.170
was you?

19:32.400 --> 19:33.130
Get in.

19:52.290 --> 19:53.440
See that mountain?

19:54.000 --> 19:54.850
He's there?

19:55.790 --> 19:56.990
Go in this direction.

19:57.090 --> 19:58.780
There's just over 40 minutes left
until the race.

19:58.780 --> 20:00.640
If you hurry, you can still make it.

20:00.640 --> 20:02.250
Find Brandy and tell him—

20:02.530 --> 20:03.730
he'll know what to do.

20:37.730 --> 20:38.960
Do you find this amusing or what?

20:38.960 --> 20:39.890
Are you ready?

20:42.500 --> 20:43.300
I'm not.

20:44.080 --> 20:45.940
I don't need to be prepared to beat you.

20:45.940 --> 20:47.140
Don't be so arrogant.

20:47.510 --> 20:49.370
Luck won't always be on your side.

20:51.110 --> 20:53.890
You can't even tell the difference
between skill and luck.

20:53.890 --> 20:55.050
I feel sorry for you.

20:55.180 --> 20:56.990
Then you'd better give it your all.

20:56.990 --> 20:58.650
Don't come up with some excuse

20:59.440 --> 21:00.610
when you lose.

21:01.000 --> 21:02.530
Only the weak make excuses.

21:02.650 --> 21:03.450
That's great.

21:03.560 --> 21:05.290
Remember to drive a bit faster.

21:05.940 --> 21:07.470
Otherwise, I'll get bored.

21:23.290 --> 21:24.050
Sanlai?

21:24.290 --> 21:25.220
What do we do now?

21:26.470 --> 21:27.200
Let me drive.

21:43.610 --> 21:44.330
Zhao.

21:44.640 --> 21:46.370
I can't let anything happen to you.

21:46.370 --> 21:47.060
Wait for me.

21:57.370 --> 21:58.170
Someone's ahead.

21:58.170 --> 21:59.500
Stop the car!

21:59.810 --> 22:00.650
Stop the car!

22:01.880 --> 22:03.190
I told you to stop!

22:04.230 --> 22:04.900
You ignorant girl!

22:04.900 --> 22:07.900
Do you even know which is the gas
and which is the brake?

22:10.130 --> 22:12.330
A woman drove up the mountain in an AE86!

22:33.290 --> 22:34.220
Why are you here?

22:34.650 --> 22:36.250
Has Jin Zhao's race started?

22:36.440 --> 22:37.260
He's in danger.

22:37.260 --> 22:39.090
We need to stop the race immediately.

22:39.090 --> 22:40.090
I know where he is.

22:40.440 --> 22:42.590
We're still a bit away
from the starting point.

22:42.590 --> 22:43.720
I'll take you there.

22:44.270 --> 22:45.470
What should we do now?

22:50.900 --> 22:52.650
What's your business here?
This road is closed.

22:52.650 --> 22:53.780
Take another route.

22:55.620 --> 22:56.770
We're here to look for someone.

22:56.770 --> 22:57.930
I've told you this road is closed.

22:57.930 --> 22:58.650
It doesn't matter
if you're looking for someone, okay?

22:58.650 --> 22:59.580
Get out of my way.

23:02.420 --> 23:03.180
Stop!

23:05.250 --> 23:06.050
Go back.

23:06.570 --> 23:08.480
Is this somewhere you're supposed to be?

23:08.480 --> 23:09.720
We need to go find Jin Zhao.

23:09.720 --> 23:10.650
Let us through.

23:10.960 --> 23:13.160
Do we know each other well or something?

23:13.250 --> 23:15.140
If you don't want him to get into trouble,

23:15.140 --> 23:16.060
then help us.

23:27.860 --> 23:29.860
He was the one who told me to get lost.

23:36.530 --> 23:37.930
He only asked you to leave

23:38.060 --> 23:39.920
because he didn't want to hurt you

23:40.200 --> 23:41.200
or get you involved

23:41.200 --> 23:42.960
in his feud with Mr. Wan.

23:45.680 --> 23:47.680
You should know better than any of us

23:47.770 --> 23:49.730
why he's been pushed to this point.

23:52.810 --> 23:54.270
You don't have to help him,

23:55.620 --> 23:56.550
unless

23:58.240 --> 24:00.300
you don't want him to survive either.

24:03.910 --> 24:05.000
Please. I beg you.

24:12.440 --> 24:13.360
Beg me?

24:14.880 --> 24:16.210
How do you want to beg me?

24:16.810 --> 24:18.200
Don't go too far.

24:19.880 --> 24:21.410
You think I'm going too far?

24:23.500 --> 24:24.360
Forget it then.

24:25.270 --> 24:26.720
Jiang Mu, let's go back
and figure something out ourselves.

24:26.720 --> 24:27.810
Name your terms!

24:29.750 --> 24:31.080
I'll agree to anything.

24:34.890 --> 24:35.690
Alright then.

24:37.050 --> 24:37.850
Kneel.

25:12.470 --> 25:13.520
Jiang Mu, get up. Let's go home.

25:13.520 --> 25:14.170
Jiang Mu!

25:14.330 --> 25:15.000
Jiang Mu, let's go home now!

25:15.000 --> 25:15.810
Don't kneel here. Get up!

25:15.810 --> 25:17.440
Jiang Mu, get up!

25:41.660 --> 25:42.660
Let them through.

25:50.490 --> 25:51.630
Move aside! Move aside!

25:51.630 --> 25:52.460
Clear the road!

25:52.460 --> 25:53.060
Move!

26:18.910 --> 26:20.470
You're too sentimental.

26:21.960 --> 26:23.020
If you keep this up,

26:23.960 --> 26:26.290
you'll have a lot of suffering ahead.

26:31.150 --> 26:32.760
But they're too late anyway.

26:51.090 --> 26:51.960
That sound...

26:52.310 --> 26:53.590
Has the race started?

27:08.720 --> 27:09.440
Brandy.

27:10.200 --> 27:11.810
You won't beat me today.

27:13.140 --> 27:14.340
We'll see about that.

27:14.620 --> 27:16.790
Beating you is way too easy.

27:26.060 --> 27:26.740
What,

27:27.380 --> 27:28.980
is this the limit of your car?

27:31.650 --> 27:33.580
Try actually surpassing me first.

28:09.310 --> 28:10.310
We can't catch up.

28:14.740 --> 28:15.580
Go up there!

28:15.770 --> 28:17.780
Sanlai, bring the Luminous Pearl
from the back seat.

28:17.780 --> 28:18.410
Okay.

28:31.270 --> 28:32.200
Where's Brandy?

28:33.000 --> 28:34.860
Why are there no cars on this road?

28:43.880 --> 28:44.940
It's Brandy's car!

28:47.700 --> 28:48.460
I saw it!

28:53.100 --> 28:55.100
Sanlai, give me the Luminous Pearl!

28:55.130 --> 28:55.720
Okay.

29:28.830 --> 29:32.790
Don't you think racing and fireworks
are similar?

29:33.680 --> 29:35.010
Both chase the light,

29:35.540 --> 29:37.740
yet fear it fleeting away in an instant.

29:38.320 --> 29:39.480
You said before

29:39.910 --> 29:42.520
that you'd sacrifice yourself
for this case.

29:43.670 --> 29:45.000
Now that you have me,

29:45.570 --> 29:48.090
has your mind changed?

29:48.570 --> 29:50.180
[Full vehicle brake system
forced shutdown due to short circuit]

29:57.200 --> 29:58.050
It's Mu.

29:58.880 --> 30:00.280
Is Mu trying to remind me?

30:57.800 --> 30:59.150
-Brandy!
-Jin Zhao!

30:59.570 --> 31:00.900
-Brandy!
-Jin Zhao!

31:00.920 --> 31:01.890
Brandy!

31:03.680 --> 31:04.960
Jin Zhao!

31:11.670 --> 31:12.390
Jiang Mu!

31:25.290 --> 31:26.530
Early this morning,

31:26.960 --> 31:28.610
a serious car accident occurred

31:28.610 --> 31:30.140
near the extension section

31:30.370 --> 31:31.810
of Highway 108 in southwest Qingshi.

31:31.810 --> 31:34.650
A car lost control due to excessive speed
and crashed off a cliff,

31:34.650 --> 31:36.720
resulting in severe damage to the vehicle.

31:36.720 --> 31:38.810
The driver's whereabouts are unknown.

31:38.810 --> 31:39.730
It is speculated that

31:39.730 --> 31:41.940
during the fall from the cliff,
the driver may have...

31:41.940 --> 31:43.830
Dad, is Zhao okay?

31:44.420 --> 31:46.550
Currently, rescue teams

31:46.640 --> 31:49.970
are intensively conducting
search and rescue operations.

31:50.040 --> 31:53.280
The specific cause of the accident
is under investigation.

31:53.280 --> 31:56.410
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

32:00.290 --> 32:03.420
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

32:25.890 --> 32:27.690
What do you mean there's no news?

32:29.240 --> 32:30.280
Tell me, what exactly are you good for?

32:30.280 --> 32:31.880
Tell me what you're good for!

32:33.370 --> 32:34.680
If he's not in the police station,
ask your uncle

32:34.680 --> 32:35.720
to check all the hospitals in Manshi

32:35.720 --> 32:36.770
and get me an clear answer!

32:36.770 --> 32:38.300
Go check all the hospitals!

32:39.640 --> 32:41.170
Go check the funeral homes!

33:02.850 --> 33:05.950
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

33:05.720 --> 33:06.520
You're awake.

33:08.660 --> 33:11.850
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

33:12.640 --> 33:15.700
♪ About your news ♪

33:14.490 --> 33:16.690
I'll take you back to Jin Qiang's place.

33:17.960 --> 33:21.610
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

33:21.890 --> 33:23.240
You must go back today.

33:23.930 --> 33:29.110
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

33:25.870 --> 33:26.940
If—I mean if—

33:29.040 --> 33:31.040
something really happened to him,

33:30.760 --> 33:34.360
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

33:33.520 --> 33:35.040
the police would call his family.

33:34.670 --> 33:39.860
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

33:41.350 --> 33:45.360
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

33:48.240 --> 33:53.360
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

33:51.890 --> 33:53.440
Jiang Mu, where are you going?

33:53.440 --> 33:55.200
I'll go find him!

33:53.720 --> 33:57.600
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

33:55.520 --> 33:57.680
We don't know where Brandy is right now!

33:57.680 --> 33:59.570
We don't know where Brandy is!

33:58.380 --> 34:04.420
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

33:59.570 --> 34:01.370
-I have to go find him!
-Jiang Mu!

34:04.870 --> 34:08.520
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

34:09.000 --> 34:13.110
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

34:13.449 --> 34:17.610
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

34:17.639 --> 34:21.570
♪ To run towards you again ♪

34:21.600 --> 34:25.020
♪ Can I hold you in my arms? ♪

34:26.010 --> 34:28.010
♪ Can you hear me ♪

34:26.639 --> 34:27.409
Jiang Mu.

34:27.929 --> 34:29.120
Don't be like this, Jiang Mu.

34:28.030 --> 34:29.850
♪ Your heart also aches, right? ♪

34:29.880 --> 34:33.590
♪ Those days and nights were not a waste ♪

34:33.610 --> 34:39.530
♪ How long will it take to answer ♪

34:42.120 --> 34:43.510
Where is he?

34:42.570 --> 34:47.120
♪ Meet the dusk with you ♪

34:43.969 --> 34:46.050
I want him back!

34:46.370 --> 34:48.639
Where is he?

34:47.330 --> 34:51.239
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

34:49.520 --> 34:51.889
I want him back!

34:51.710 --> 34:57.100
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

34:58.600 --> 35:02.270
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

35:02.290 --> 35:06.690
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

35:06.860 --> 35:08.860
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

35:09.040 --> 35:10.750
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

35:10.780 --> 35:14.210
♪ To run towards you again ♪

35:15.130 --> 35:19.220
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

35:20.830 --> 35:24.480
♪ For a lifetime ♪

35:45.770 --> 35:46.960
Go get some rest.

35:51.190 --> 35:52.100
Don't worry.

35:52.720 --> 35:54.280
Zhao will be fine.

35:54.770 --> 35:56.000
Your father and I will keep watch.

35:56.000 --> 35:57.130
If there's any news,

35:57.410 --> 35:58.870
we'll tell you right away.

37:52.770 --> 37:53.610
Jiang Mu.

37:58.890 --> 38:01.420
I've checked with all the hospitals
in Manshi

38:01.480 --> 38:03.010
and the surrounding areas,

38:04.320 --> 38:05.980
but there's no news of Brandy.

38:12.180 --> 38:13.010
But, Jiang Mu,

38:14.070 --> 38:16.130
given the current situation, no news

38:17.850 --> 38:19.110
is actually good news.

38:27.420 --> 38:28.280
Have you eaten?

38:34.090 --> 38:34.840
Come on.

39:03.610 --> 39:04.470
Eat something.

39:04.800 --> 39:07.240
We still have to
keep searching for Brandy later.

39:07.240 --> 39:09.040
Don't pass out from exhaustion.

39:41.120 --> 39:42.320
Slow down. Slow down.

39:43.250 --> 39:44.230
Don't eat like that.

39:44.230 --> 39:46.190
Slow down! Don't eat like that!

39:46.700 --> 39:47.740
Jiang Mu!

39:55.770 --> 39:56.690
Jiang Mu!

40:00.810 --> 40:01.850
Stop eating!
